{"tid":556984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔九巴翻側 邪門2月10日 曾發生港鐵縱火案1死8傷及八仙嶺山火5死13傷","createTime":"2018-02-11T02:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T03:39:51.000Z","uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"816a3850c9dd3f93428866422a3540d3f22cb6b7","tid":556984,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"大埔公路傍晚發生造成至少18死62人傷的嚴重事故，無獨有偶，今日亦是釀成1死18人傷的港鐵縱火事故一周年，而在22年前轟動全港、導致5死13傷的八仙嶺山火，同樣於2月10日發生。 <br />\n<br />\n2017年2月10日晚上7時13分，一列荃灣綫往荃灣方向的列車，經海底隧道前往尖沙咀站，第一卡一名張姓(60歲)男乘客，期間不斷喃喃自語，並突然高呼「我要燒死晒你哋！」，其後更取出載有易燃液體的酒樽，向自己及身旁乘客淋潑，並用打火機點火自焚，有乘客走避不及，身上衣物被燒著，皮膚亦被燒傷。連張在內，事件造成19人受傷，當中4人情況一度危殆。而張則因嚴重燒傷，留醫3個月後，於5月14日因器官衰竭不治。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，1996年今日中午，馬鞍山馮堯敬紀念中學49名學生及5名老師到八仙嶺行山，期間有人疑吸煙後遺下煙頭引發火警，火勢迅速沿山上方向蔓延，師生需攀過石壁逃生，2名老師在協助大部分學生攀過石壁後，因趕不及逃離而葬身火海，事件中亦造成另外3名學生喪生，13人受傷。"},{"pid":"554ebe592bcc5f446276ff293cde783559d6d61f","tid":556984,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"可能2月10係deadline<br />\n下面要交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a596a24520561e2c5422f0dcd9a138e1d8f1360","tid":556984,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"228342afd91087faa86f52c1e6fc55f02fee3cd0","tid":556984,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a596a24520561e2c5422f0dcd9a138e1d8f1360","tid":556984,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"554ebe592bcc5f446276ff293cde783559d6d61f","tid":556984,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"可能2月10係deadline<br />\n下面要交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"只係知96同18既2月10號都係星期六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2354beba2e1516ba46362ee4ff59408fb446620","tid":556984,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"228342afd91087faa86f52c1e6fc55f02fee3cd0","tid":556984,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a596a24520561e2c5422f0dcd9a138e1d8f1360","tid":556984,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"554ebe592bcc5f446276ff293cde783559d6d61f","tid":556984,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T02:59:28.000Z","msg":"可能2月10係deadline<br />\n下面要交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:02:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"只係知96同18既2月10號都係星期六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2757404a319e88b62a344abf1a915eec9f66f9b3","tid":556984,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:22:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2622fab2d6e3afef6ee923d35a85cc06e3b41183","tid":556984,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7860951da739218fe500974dd445ffcb4b4da626","tid":556984,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d473d71bdafa8c31b3caba3c2fbe8d7c4ba3adb0","tid":556984,"uid":69177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"痕仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}